By Representative Higgins of Leominster, a petition (accompanied by bill, House, No. 1438) of
Natalie M. Higgins, Lindsay N. Sabadosa and James B. Eldridge that the student loan
ombudsman establish a live annual training program for all state employees regarding eligibility
for the Public Service Loan Forgiveness Program through the U.S. Department of Education.
