In the One Hundred and Ninety-Fourth General Court
(2025-2026)
_______________
An Act increasing awareness of public student loan forgiveness.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Section 35 of Chapter 12 of the General Laws is hereby amended by adding the following
2 in subsection (b):-
3 The student loan ombudsman in coordination with the human services division within the
4 executive office for administration and finance shall assist in establishing a live annual training
5 program for all state employees regarding their eligibility for the Public Service Loan
6 Forgiveness Program through the U.S. Department of Education. An online training module shall
7 be provided during all new state employee onboarding.
